      <title>沙特阿美首席执行官称石油需求强劲，近期抛售是反应过度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/aramco-ceo-says-oil-demand-is-strong-and-recent-selloff-was-overreaction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大原油出口商沙特阿美表示，由于市场对经济形势不佳而导致的全球石油市场抛售有些过度，因为需求依然强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/aramco-ceo-says-oil-demand-is-strong-and-recent-selloff-was-overreaction</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 11:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
